# Career Goals

+Careers

## Criteria

1. Linux command line every day
1. Lots of programming
1. High paying senior roles (50k+)
1. Possibility of remote working

## End Goal: *DevOps/Site Reliability Engineer*

## Entry Points:

1. Development
	1. Software developmer
1. Operations
	1. System administrator/engineer
	1. Network administrator/engineer
	1. Security analyst

## What's the best entry point?

Front-end web development is the nearest port in the unemployment storm,
however an apprenticeship (ideally in operations) is more prefereable.

